FieldOfView: Field of View of the camera in degrees
AspectRatio: Aspect Ratio of the camera (Width / Heigth)
Aperture: Aperture of the camera in terms of f-stop
FocusDistance: Focus distance of the camera in cm. Works only in manual focus method
ProjectionMode: ProjectionMode of the camera (Perspective, Orthographic, etc...)
PropertyValues: Values of the properties defined in the static structure. Use FLiveLinkBaseStaticData.FindPropertyValue to evaluate.
